    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/a8a2f3223f2b84b5fbfdd31e697e9f5c.poster.avif?t=1749318828\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/a8a2f3223f2b84b5fbfdd31e697e9f5c.webm?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/a8a2f3223f2b84b5fbfdd31e697e9f5c.mp4?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一座神秘的金字塔出现在埃及那片无情沙漠的中心。关于隐藏在诅咒墓室里的无尽财富的低语声吸引了世界各地的考古学家和冒险者。你不是学者，你是盗墓者，而时间已经不多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/691a4201fe6eabd832b2826e223f7160.poster.avif?t=1749318828\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/691a4201fe6eabd832b2826e223f7160.webm?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/691a4201fe6eabd832b2826e223f7160.mp4?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《沙之秘契》中，你将深入金字塔的阴暗走廊，遇到奇异的人物，挑战致命的陷阱和谜题。古老的诅咒和不安的灵魂潜伏在黑暗中，等待下一个闯入者的到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/e0de6dfe30aa0a1996fbcf843b1007bd.poster.avif?t=1749318828\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/e0de6dfe30aa0a1996fbcf843b1007bd.webm?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/e0de6dfe30aa0a1996fbcf843b1007bd.mp4?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这座金字塔不仅仅隐藏着宝藏——它还蕴藏着那些曾来过此地的人的冰冷遗迹。前人留下的足迹暗示着什么？在法老的古墓下，隐藏着怎样的黑暗阴谋？时空的界限扭曲变幻，将那些毫无准备的人困在永恒的黑暗之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/6fa87427c07f346d8d0c34a351894cb7.poster.avif?t=1749318828\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/6fa87427c07f346d8d0c34a351894cb7.webm?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325160/extras/6fa87427c07f346d8d0c34a351894cb7.mp4?t=1749318828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能智胜重重危险，揭开传说中的宝藏，还是将成为沙漠下又一位迷失的灵魂？</p>",
